      "autoClaim:1": 0,
      "desc:8": "The Timewood Clock is a special block that can be obtained in The Twilight Forest. It can be used to accelerate vanilla crops in a 16 block radius, making farms significantly faster and more efficient.\n\nTo get one, you must explore inside the massive Twilight Forest trees and search the loot chests hidden within them. There is a small chance to find a Tree of Time sapling. The clock generates hidden inside the tree after it grows.\n[warn]\nAfter growing the tree, you will need a Silk Touch tool to obtain the Timewood Clock itself.[/warn]\n[note]\nIf you break it without Silk Touch, it will instead drop several vanilla gold clocks.\n[/note]",
